    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc_vm.00197_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <date when="1880-04-13" rend="right"><hi rend="underline">Tuesday evening</hi>
                        April 13<ptr target="loc.03993_n1"/></date>
                </dateline>
            </opener>

            <p>Harry, if come up Thursday (say by the 5.13 p m train) go up to the hall by 7 oclock,
                and make yourself useful, if you feel like it&#8212;Give this note to the one it is
                address'd to<ptr target="loc.03993_n2"/>&#8212;ask for him there&#8212;(I will
                mention it to him&#8212;he is bossing the thing for me)&#8212;act as usher, or door
                keeper, or help in the box office&#8212;it will be fun for you&#8212;</p>

            <closer>
                <signed rend="right">Walt</signed>
            </closer>
